                     <interp inst="t18470614-1422-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> stealing 1 basket, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 loaf of bread, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. the goods of <persName id="t18470614-name-531" type="victimName">
