                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi> 199.) I produce a certificate of Simpson's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted on the</hi> 17<hi rend="italic">th of August, 1846, having been before convicted, and confined nine months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
